/* =========================================================================
   boss.js — Boss Mode question bank (full Paper-2-style mock)
   The generator in app.js builds a fresh 90-mark paper each time:
   ≥1×12, ≥2×9, ≥4×6 and short (1–4 mark) questions (~50% long / 50% short).
   ALL questions are drawn strictly from CO4–CO8 content.
   Long questions are marked with the levels grids in data.js (LEVELS).
   ========================================================================= */
